WHAT IS IT?

   An isometric game engine.


CONTROLS
       arrow keys  move the cursor/subcursor in the plane
       with shift  move soldier
        pgup/down  move the cursor/subcursor vertically
       numpad, or  
         qweadzxc  put/remove a wall in one direction (se below), at the cursor
	    space  toggle floor: block/half-block/floor/nothing
	      r/t  rotate the whole view by +/-90 degrees
	      k/l  Save/load level. Filename input from the terminal.
                   
